               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols. 11ra-36vb)
 II)
                     Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 36vb-105vb), incomplete
                     - Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     45rb-52rb) 
 - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.
                     60va-65ra)
 
 Additiones 1-4.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text II is called Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat on <locus target="#11ra">11ra</locus>.</note>
                     <note>- Text III is called Maṣḥafa fǝtḥat in the incipit on <locus target="#36vb">36vb</locus>.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
